We start the evolution at a scale  and move towards the infrared.
The initial condition is given by eqs. (), (), and
corresponds to a system in the broken phase.
We observe that initially  is small, because of the
smallness of the value of  we chose. Subsequently the 
potential evolves (dashed lines), while its minimum  remains
